.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: purple, lilac, blood-red, mauve, amber
Nationality: american, mexican, turkish, malaysian, russian
Beverage: juice, iced-cola, almond-milk, cola, sprite
Cigar: purplemaster, baccarat, bongani, chaman, vegafina
Pet: hamster, turtle, goldpony, pony, goat
1. Nationality:american == Color:blood-red
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:goldpony
3. Nationality:mexican == Beverage:cola
4. Color:lilac is on the left of Color:mauve
5. Color:lilac == Beverage:iced-cola
6. Cigar:bongani == Pet:turtle
7. Color:amber == Cigar:baccarat
8. Beverage:almond-milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:malaysian is on the far left
10. Cigar:vegafina is on the left or right of Pet:hamster
11. Pet:goats is on the left or right of Cigar:baccarat
12. Cigar:purplemaster == Beverage:juice
13. Nationality:turkish == Cigar:chaman
14. Nationality:malaysian is on the left or right of Color:purple
15. Cigar:vegafina is on the left or right of Beverage:sprite

